## Frontmatter schemas

**Weekly report** (`type: weekly-report`): `date`, `range`, `site`, `sessions`, `users`, `page_views`, `begin_checkout`, `purchases`, `revenue_usd`, `source`.

**Campaign** (`type: campaign`): `channel`, `product`, `status`, `target_cpa`, `utm_campaign`, `utm_source`, `utm_medium`, `landing_pages`.

## Report generation

Run from repo root:

```bash
node scripts/marketing-weekly-report.mjs
node scripts/marketing-weekly-report.mjs --range 28d --force
```

Writes `marketing-vault/03-reports/weekly/YYYY-MM-DD.md`. Uses the same GA4 env vars as `/admin/analytics.html`.

