When adding a new campaign landing page in `public/`, update or create the matching note in `02-campaigns/<product>/` with UTM fields and link to [[05-playbooks/weekly-review-process]].

## Site tracking (Be Certified Today)

- Attribution: `public/js/campaign-attribution.js` (UTM + gclid â†’ GA4).
- Checkout events: `data-bcc-track="begin_checkout"` on checkout controls.
- Admin dashboard: `public/admin/analytics.html` + `api/analytics-report.js`.

Link new paid traffic to campaign notes via `utm_campaign` matching `02-campaigns/*/*.md` frontmatter.

## Website optimization (Google Ads quality)

Landing page edits for ad quality live in `06-website-optimization/`. When the user changes ad landing content in `public/`:

1. Follow `marketing-vault/01-strategy/positioning-and-messaging.md`: **exam prep**, not training/courses; emphasize realistic practice, verified solutions, no PDF/third-party software.
2. Update the matching page note under `06-website-optimization/pages/` (hero copy, audit scores).
3. Append a row to `06-website-optimization/content-change-log.md` with date, path, summary, and campaign.
4. Preserve message match: ad keywords â†’ H1/hero; align FAQ facts with `01-strategy/google-ai-search-strategy.md`.
5. Do not use misleading certification claims (â€śguaranteed passâ€ť, implied CompTIA endorsement, dump/cheat language).
